Package: sensortowerR
Title: An R Interface to the 'Sensor Tower' API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Phillip",
           family = "Black",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "pblack@gameeconomistconsulting.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A wrapper for the 'Sensor Tower' API. The package provides functions to interact with the API to fetch mobile app analytics data, including app information, publisher details, revenue and download estimates, and active user metrics.
